Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.76,Default,Ush,0,0,0,,Už jdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:44.52,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,Jdeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.27,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,Hej, Ushio! {ep 19}
